                        <note rend="inline" type="source">818.6363/114: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Costa Rica</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Davis</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-13T17:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">May 13,
                                        1922—5 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>8. Your 18, May 8, 9 A.M.</p>
                        <p>You may make representations in accordance with Department’s 7, May 5, 3
                            P.M.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
